POST {{baseUrl}}/step
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action_type": "do_magic",
  "order_id": "O1"
}

### Missing required fields for route_order
POST {{baseUrl}}/step
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action_type": "route_order",
  "order_id": "O201"
}

### Non-existent entity
POST {{baseUrl}}/step
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action_type": "inspect_order",
  "order_id": "O9999"
}
